column5: for those of you that like this reel they are on sale at CTC for $50 and Nanofil is $16.  just read the flyer
How is that for timing, my Cabelas 10ft whuppin stick for perch fishing just arrived today!!! Wanted to pair it up with a President now I can save some cash!!!!
Lindsay Crappie Tire has my name all over it this weekend. I'm gonna check out the kayak for $120 off too.
the presidents are a great reel for the money for sure!  S.
